OL,3,C'Unsafe practices' highlighted in
OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,FAn independent report has highlighted
OL,7,Fa handful of shortcomings in Jersey's
OL,8,FNeurology department.
OL,10,FAmong the concerns raised were "unsafe
OL,11,Fpractices", "unmanageable workloads"
OL,12,Fand "overstretched" staff.
OL,14,FJersey's General Hospital called for
OL,15,Fthe review to be carried out, with
OL,16,Frepresentatives from the Royal College
OL,17,Fof Physicians (RCP) visiting the
OL,18,Fisland early last year to interview
OL,19,Fstaff.
