OL,6,FThey made several suggestions for
OL,7,Fimprovement, with some of the key
OL,8,Frecommendations being:
OL,10,FAs part of the review, the RCP looked
OL,11,Fat the cases of 12 patients who
OL,12,Freceived treatment in the department.
OL,14,FSeven of their cases were graded as
OL,15,F'good practice' - but the other five
OL,16,Fwere found to have 'needed
OL,17,Fimprovement'.
