OL,3,C'Unsafe practices' highlighted in
OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,FSophie Reid has a Grade Three
OL,7,FAstrocytoma - a fast-growing,
OL,8,Fmalignant, high-grade brain tumour,
OL,9,Fwhich in her case, is terminal.
OL,11,FDespite that diagnosis, Sophie has
OL,12,Frecently undergone treatment which
OL,13,Fcould help to prolong her life - but
OL,14,Fsays she feels let down by the
OL,15,Fhospital.
