OL,3,C'Unsafe practices' highlighted in
OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,FAfter presenting at A&E following a
OL,7,Fseizure, she was sent home without
OL,8,Fhaving a CT - it was not until she
OL,9,Fwent to her GP and requested an urgent
OL,10,Fscan that doctors found her brain
OL,11,Ftumour.
OL,13,FWhen she received the call at work
OL,14,Fthat doctors had found legions on her
OL,15,Fbrain, Sophie says she felt "disgusted
OL,16,Fand quite traumatised".
OL,18,FShe adds: "I was very much thinking,
OL,19,F'surely this is going to be nothing'.
