OL,3,C'Unsafe practices' highlighted in
OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,F"My mind went straight to my little
OL,7,Fgirls. How was I going to tell my
OL,8,Ffriends and family?
OL,10,F"I feel like as a community, the
OL,11,FJersey brain tumour community, we're
OL,12,Fso let down. We have so many fights we
OL,13,Fhave to make and have to advocate for
OL,14,Fourselves. I do believe if we don't
OL,15,Fstart advocating for ourselves, then
OL,16,Fchange isn't going to happen.
