OL,3,C'Unsafe practices' highlighted in
OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,F"I feel like it's a fight I shouldn't
OL,7,Fbe fighting. We pay our social
OL,8,Fsecurity contributions, we pay our
OL,9,Ftaxes, and yet we're still having to
OL,10,Ffight for ourselves; there's no one
OL,11,Fthere to fight for us."
OL,13,FIn response to the review, Simon West
OL,14,F- the Executive Director of Health at
OL,15,FJersey General Hospital - tells ITV
OL,16,FNews that the department will
OL,17,Fimplement the College's findings.
