OL,6,FHe explains: "I think it's a very
OL,7,Fpositive report and paints a very good
OL,8,Fpicture of the services that we
OL,9,Fdeliver in Jersey from a neurology
OL,10,Fperspective.
OL,12,F"For those patients who are worried
OL,13,Fabout anything that is in the report,
OL,14,FI would encourage them to reach out to
OL,15,Four PALS (Patient Advice and Liaison)
OL,16,Fservice, who will connect with myself
OL,17,For other members of our staff who will
OL,18,Fbe able to direct them accordingly and
OL,19,Fhear what they have to say.
