OL,6,F"For those patients who are already in
OL,7,Fthe system, who are genuinely
OL,8,Fconcerned about any aspect of their
OL,9,Fcare, I'd encourage them to speak to
OL,10,Fthe feedback team so that we can
OL,11,Fensure their concerns are met and
OL,12,Faddressed."
