OL,4,CJersey Neurology report
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister, Deputy Tom
OL,7,FBinet, adds: "I was pleased to see
OL,8,Fthat the review highlighted a strong
OL,9,Fcommitment across the neurology team,
OL,10,Fsenior management, as well as the
OL,11,FMinisterial team to improve services
OL,12,Fand it also found that there were
OL,13,Fsolid foundations in place to support
OL,14,Fpatient outcomes.
OL,16,F"Following the recommendations
OL,17,Foutlined in the review, an action plan
OL,18,Fhas been drawn up and two of the
OL,19,Factions have already been completed.
